{{Otheruses|Sleeper}}
[[File:XizorsBed-SOTE.jpg|thumb|right|200px|One of the many beds in [[Prince/Legends|Prince]] [[Xizor/Legends|Xizor's]] [[Xizor's Palace|palace]]]]
A '''sleeper''', alternatively known in other variations as a '''bed''', '''sleep couch''', or '''cot''', was a piece of furniture or location that was used primarily as a place to [[Sleep/Legends|sleep]]. Some took the form of solid or semi-solid mattresses, or '''sleep mats''', while others could mold themselves to the being who slept upon them and react to their movements.

The sheets of a bed might be printed with elaborate designs, and children's bed linen often featured war heroes and villains of the galaxy.<ref name="SWG">{{GalaxiesNGE}}</ref>

